name: Mba005 When Harry met Sally (The Oliver Collection)
description:
Have you ever watched Cinderella and got jelous of her relationship with her avian friends who dressed her for the ball?!!

No more!  You can have your own little fascinating pidgeon-pair bird-fellows to nest in your hair, braids or buns.. all of the above!  A great alternative to fascinators during the Racing Season, or a new take on a friendship bracelet!

Sold as a pair, Mister Harry and Miss Sally are made of foam and delicate chocolate brown duck feathers and black maribou, these little babies are attached to 4cm ribbon covered alligator clips to attach to your hair or headband or outfit!

Shake your tail feathers!
